ActImmigration and Refugee Protection Act
PrecisReappointment of LOIS DELIA FIGG of Toronto, Ontario, as a full-time member of the Immigration and Refugee Board (Toronto Regional Office), to hold office during good behaviour for a term of one year; and designation of LOIS DELIA FIGG to be Assistant Deputy Chairperson of the Immigration and Refugee Board (Toronto Regional Office); effective June 26, 2012.
